resources.string: Chikamu chino chinotumira panowanikwa chombo chino kushamwari yako. Akavhura inobva yatanga nguva yekugoverana sikirini
Paunofambisa chombo chiri parunharembozha, sikirini yeshamwari yako inobva yaitawo saizvozvo. Zvinotendera kuti mufambirane pamafoni ari maviri panguva imwechete.
Tumira chiziviso kumunhu mumwe kana vakawanda kuti mutange chikamu chekugoverana sikirini.
